* Row-Based Formats\n(CSV / JSON)
** Valid Use Cases
***_ Landing zone (initial ingestion)
***_ Small data volumes
***_ Source system only exports text
***_ Human-readable debugging
** Limitations
***_ Poor analytical performance
***_ No ACID transactions
***_ No time travel
***_ High parse overhead
** Best Practice
***_ Convert to Delta Lake during ingestion
***_ Don't store analytics data as CSV/JSON
@endmindmap
